steps.name: Go to Database and get First name and Last name of employees who works in Europe and validate with their UI information (First name, Last Name).
Go to Excel and update column ‘Actual # of Employees’ with number of Europe employees that you get from UI.
Compare ‘Actual # of Employees’’ with ‘expected # of Employees’ and if they matched then update ‘Test Execution Status’ cell as PASSED if not match then update with FAILED.
